snippet.title: Love Angel Syndrome - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
"It's a white void, with shifting lines of binary as far as the eye can see. It's nothing and everything at the same time. My beginning and my end."

For the past two months I've had the incredible opportunity to work on a soundtrack for a gamejam project for Lilybyte Studios! The game is called Love Angel Syndrome and I'm so proud to showcase everything we've created so far! If the project does well we'll consider the idea of turning it into a full lenght game so please go over there and show them your support!
THE GAME IS FREE TO PLAY ON ITCH.IO, PLEASE CHECK IT OUT!
https://ladyoph3lia.itch.io/loveangelsyndrome
